15,01Music deafens
15,01Color blinds
15,01Electricity 
15,01Has killed your mind.

15,01Feeling through doorways
15,01Grasping at air
15,01The fast lane quickens
15,01And leaves you behind.

15,01Tasting the fresh earth
15,01Smelling new life
15,01Suddenly blackness
15,01In touch, smell
15,01Hearing and sight.

15,01Never again
15,01To know this sweet world
15,01As you toss and tumble
15,01Through grey nightmare swirls.

15,01Waking up hopeless
15,01In wonder and awe
15,01Hoping to see
15,01One final dawn.

15,01Bul all that is left
15,01Untainted, untouched
15,01Are the greatest of truths
15,01Which no one dared speak.

15,01Before man's molding's 
15,01Of wood, steel and rock
15,01Stood Nature's true beauties
15,01Chaos, disorder
15,01And greater than all
15,01Relentless HAVOK.

15,01                Zaphod [Havok]
